name: RocketX Hybrid Exchange
shortDescription: RocketX aggregates 250+ CEXs & DEXS to get users the best rates & lowest fees for ANY trade!
description: RocketX is the FIRST “Multi-Chain” CEX & DEX aggregator that helps users swap ANY token on ANY chain with the best rates across 250+ exchanges. RocketX enhances interoperability between blockchains & simplifies Multi-Chain trading by enabling CROSS-CHAIN SWAP and BRIDGE of native assets at One-Click across leading networks via a single intuitive UI.
